This e-learning platform is a modern, responsive web application designed to teach HTML, CSS, and JavaScript in a visually stunning and user-friendly way. It features a sleek landing page with smooth gradients, animated course cards, and intuitive navigation. Each course has its own dedicated page with a structured curriculum, progress tracking, and easy enrollment functionality. The design follows mobile-first principles, ensuring a flawless experience on phones, tablets, and desktops. Built with clean HTML, CSS, and vanilla JavaScript, the site delivers fast performance without relying on heavy frameworks, and is hosted on Vercel for seamless accessibility.
